      • makePattern

        static ParameterPattern makePattern​(java.lang.String delimiter,
                                    java.util.List<ParameterName> parameterNames,
                                    java.util.List<Parameter> parameters)
        Creates a ParameterPattern. A ParameterPattern object has only delimiter, but no regex. The reason is that every Parameter has its own, so only a delimiter is needed to concatenate them.
        Parameters:
        delimiter - character sequence delimiter
        parameterNames - the names of parameters
        parameters - ParameterName and Parameter bindings in sequential order
        Returns:
        a ParameterPattern object
        Since:
        0.1
